<mvc:View 
	controllerName="com.sap.sapmentors.HTML5UserAPIforCF-ui.controller.Home" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
	xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
	displayBlock="true"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Shell id="shell">
		<App id="app">
			<pages>
				<Page id="page" title="{i18n>title}">
					<l:VerticalLayout
						class="sapUiContentPadding"
						width="100%">
						<l:content>
							<Link
								text="/services/userapi/currentUser"
								href="/services/userapi/currentUser" />
						</l:content>
					</l:VerticalLayout>
				</Page>
			</pages>
		</App>
	</Shell>
</mvc:View>